			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Sanggamte aw, note’ theih dingin i pupi David’ thu a teltakin kong gen ding hi. Amah si-in kivui a, a han zong tu mahmahin eite kiangah omlai hi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> David pen kamsang hi a, ama tunga Pasian’ thuciam a thei hi. Ama suante khat, amah bang teek mahin kumpi-in a bawl nading Pasian in thu a ciam hi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Pasian in a sep ding thu David in mukhol ahih manin, ‘Mi site gam sungah amah kinusia lo a, a sa a muat kei hi,’ ci-in a gen ciangin, Khrih’ thawhkik nading thu a gengen ahi hi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Pasian in sihna panin hih Jesuh hingkiksak a, kote khempeuh pen hih thu a thei teci vive ka hi uh hi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Amah in Pasian’ taklamah omna dongin liatna ngah a, ama tungah Pasian in a ciamsa Kha Siangtho zong a ngahkhin hi. Tu laitak a na muh na zak uh nate pen kote tungah a hong piak tua Kha Siangtho ahi hi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> David pen vantungah a kahtoh loh hangin amah in, ‘Topa in keima Topa kiangah: Na khe nuai-ah na galte kong koihsak matengin ka taklamah na tu in, ci-in gen hi,’ ci hi.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Tua ahih ciangin singlamteh tungah na thah uh hih Jesuh pen Pasian in Topa le Khrih in a bawl khitna thu, Israel mi khempeuh in teltakin thei ta un,” a ci hi.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Amaute in hih thu a zak uh ciangin a lungsim uh nakpitakin sukha a, Peter le sawltak dangte kiangah, “Sanggamte aw, bangci gamtat ding ka hi uh hiam?” ci-in a dong uh hi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Tua ciangin Peter in amaute kiangah, “Na mawhna uh kisik unla, na mawhna uh hong kimaisak theih nadingin Jesuh Khrih min tawh tui kiphum ciat un. Tua hileh Pasian’ piakkhong Kha Siangtho na ngah ding uh hi.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bang hang hiam cih leh Pasian in ama kamciamna pen note tung, na suan na khakte uh tung le gamlapi-a om mi khempeuh, i Topa Pasian in a sap mi khempeuh tungah a hong bawl ahi hi,” ci-in a dawng hi.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Tua ciangin Peter in amaute tungah thu tampi genthuahin hanthawn a, “Hih migilote’ gimthuak ding na tuahkhak loh nadingun nomau mah in na suahtak nading uh lampi zong ciat un,” a ci hi.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Mi tampi in ama thugen umin tui kiphum uh a, tua ni-in mihing tulthum bang kibehlap uh hi.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Amaute in sawltakte tung panin thu sinin amaute tawh kikhawl uh a, amaute tawh an nekhawmin, thu zong a ngenkhawm uh hi.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Sawltakte in lim le nalamdang tampi bawl uh a, mi khempeuh in lamdang sa mahmah uh hi.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Thu um khempeuh kikhawlin omkhawm uh a, a neihsate uh zong a neikhawm uh hi.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Amaute in a neih a lamteng uh zuak uh a, a sumte pen amau kisapna tawh kizui-in amaute lakah a hawm uh hi.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Nisimin biakinn-ah kikhawm uh a, a innte uhah an nekhawmin, lungdamna le kiniamkhiatna tawh a ne ciat uh hi.",
